data.description: New Price for the New Year! Are you looking for a home in a 55+ community in Groveland, Florida? If so, you will love this well-maintained and upgraded home with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms plus a flex den/office. This property has it all! More space and more upgrades for your money.   Here are some of the features of this home:  - The home is located in **Trilogy**, aka Cascades of Groveland, a gated resort-style community that offers a variety of amenities and activities for active adults including pool, fitness center, tennis, pickleball, bocce courts, event center, card room, sports room, and artisan studio.   - The home has a spacious open floor plan with **2017 square feet** of living space. One of the largest plans in this phase, and a **two-car garage**. Featuring extra storage and epoxy floors.   - The home features a **gourmet kitchen** with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, 42-inch cabinets, and a large island. Separate pantry and extra large storage area in the laundry room.   - The home has a **primary suite** with a walk-in closet, dual sinks, and a walk-in shower.  - The home has a **guest bedroom** with a full bathroom and a **den** that can be used as an office or a hobby room.  - The home has **many upgrades** such as recessed lighting, ceiling fan on front porch, custom closet system, iWave ion generator on hvac system, Ring doorbell, Nest Thermostat, and plantation shutters throughout.  - Enlarged and completely screened**covered lanai** with a ceiling fan and an extended patio with pavers.  - Extensive upgraded**low-maintenance landscaping** with irrigation system and curbing.  Compare the price per square foot in the neighborhood. Possibly the best deal in Trilogy!  Don't miss this opportunity to own your dream home in Trilogy!
